org.openscience.cdk
Interface CDKConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
AtomPlacer, ChemObject, CMLReader, CMLWriter, ConnectivityChecker, HasInformation, HOSECodeGenerator, MDLReader, MDLWriter, PathTools, Projector, RingPlacer, StructureDiagramGenerator
public interface CDKConstants

An interface providing predefined values for a number of parameters used throughout the cdk. Classes using these Constants should implement this interface.
